{"tid":960673,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【再剃眼眉？】ViuTV撼贏無綫製作除夕倒數活動 搵林子祥及《造星》囝囝撐場","createTime":"2018-12-29T15:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T16:33:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"25802f0fc755e5a174526c8dd09ef00fc681d231","tid":960673,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T15:03:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181228/59080169\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59080169&d=Uy2xpkpjBMQV3%2BMr4GcBXbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=f85cbdcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181228%2F59080169&h=bcac62a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181228/59080169</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月28日 <br />\n<br />\n【再剃眼眉？】ViuTV撼贏無綫製作除夕倒數活動 搵林子祥及《造星》囝囝撐場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181228/large/1545989559_3b78.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181228%2Flarge%2F1545989559_3b78.jpg&h=5f8534a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nViuTV撼贏無綫做倒數及煙花直播。<br />\n建立時間 (HKT): 1228 17:22<br />\n<br />\n以前乜嘢大型活動都畀無綫包攬播映權，但隨住另一免費電視ViuTV嘅出現，對大台成威脅。除咗今年4月舉行嘅香港電影金像獎頒獎典禮，ViuTV撼贏無綫攞到獨家播映權之外，早幾個月嘅俄羅斯世界盃，ViuTV亦攞咗香港免費電視獨家播映權，佢哋直播多場賽事都有高收視，遠遠拋離咗無綫。<br />\n<br />\n估唔到2018年完結之前，ViuTV再嚟多鑊，就係今個月31日晚11點喺尖沙嘴文化中心外舉行嘅「香港除夕倒數」，ViuTV首次撼贏無綫攞到製作同直播播映權。呢個除夕倒數同放煙花大型活動，係由香港旅遊發展局搞，然後公開畀人投標搞製作同直播，過去10年都係無綫投得，無綫今次亦志在必得，點知今年畀ViuTV投到。<br />\n<br />\n據《蘋果》了解，由於睇倒數煙花多數係年青人，所以ViuTV投標時就針對呢點，走年青人方向，另一樣嘢，係大台每年都要收旅發局好大筆製作費，聽講係數百萬，今次ViuTV開出個價錢畀大台低，喺呢兩個原因下，ViuTV咪中標囉，聽聞大台管理層對今次畀ViuTV搶飯碗嬲到震呢！<br />\n<br />\nViuTV噚晚已經喺facebook上載咗除夕當晚宣傳片，表演嘉賓有林子祥、AGA等等之外，當然唔少得佢哋喺《全民造星》打造出嚟嘅新男團Mirror同Error啦，Mirror同Error勁多fans，睇怕到時一定迫爆文化中心呢！<br />\n<br />\n對此ViuTV公關今日回應《蘋果》話:「ViuTV非常高興今年能夠與香港旅遊發展局第一次合作《香港除夕倒數》。當晚出席的歌手包括有林子祥、劉卓昕、AGA、駱振偉、黃劍文、男子組合Mirror及 Error，將會載歌載舞，以精彩的表演同香港觀眾歡度除夕，迎接新的一年。ViuTV99台及網上平台將於31號晚上11時直播現場盛況。」<br />\n<br />\n精選娛聞，喺晒《娛果》<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.com/appledailyent\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.com%2Fappledailyent&d=Uy2xpkpjBMQV3%2BMr4GcBXbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=3a965e73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://fb.com/appledailyent</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181228/large/1545988723_9fba.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181228%2Flarge%2F1545988723_9fba.jpg&h=9f11cc64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林子祥擔任表演嘉賓。(ViuTV截圖)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181228/large/1545988724_191b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181228%2Flarge%2F1545988724_191b.jpg&h=d5ee8cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMirror嘅出現一定吸引大班fans到場。(資料圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181228/large/1545988728_f8f2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181228%2Flarge%2F1545988728_f8f2.jpg&h=b20649f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nError又有份出騷啦。(網上圖片)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181228/large/1545988728_135f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181228%2Flarge%2F1545988728_135f.jpg&h=81d0fa28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nAGA係表演嘉賓之一。(ViuTV截圖)"},{"pid":"517560b354415af0f28d3d3b75eaaf1f271bcfa1","tid":960673,"uid":132587,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T15:11:18.000Z","msg":"年年煙花同隊乜柒mirror一樣 都係多鳩餘"},{"pid":"6dbe1ec6bf48cc11fc701d56e0f9cfc7c6384599","tid":960673,"uid":36911,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-29T16:33:00.000Z","msg":"年年幾場煙花<br />\n仲有後生仔睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}